## **3. Design Principles**

### **3.1 Minimalistic Design**

* Clean lines, white space, flat layout
* Simple color palette (Primary + Accent + Neutral)
* Only one main action per screen
* Reduce cognitive load

### **3.2 Accessibility First**

* Large buttons
* Icon-based navigation
* Audio for all content
* Low text dependency
* Suitable for users with low literacy

### **3.3 Mobile-First Experience**

* Designed for mobile web
* Fast loading and optimized for low bandwidth
* Thumb-friendly navigation (bottom bar)

### **3.4 Motivation & Gamification**

* XP points
* Streaks
* Badges
* Progress tracking
* Simple and fun animations

